snippet.title: TrickStyle + Beats (Criterion Games - Dreamcast - 1999)
snippet.description:
"TrickStyle is a sports video game developed by Criterion Games and published by Acclaim Entertainment for the Dreamcast and Microsoft Windows. Set in the future, the player takes part in stunt-filled hoverboard races through London, Tokyo, and Manhattan, or inside a massive arena called the Velodrome."

game info: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/TrickStyle
